Signed-off-by: Mike Leach <mike.leach@linaro.org>
Reviewed-and-tested-by: Suzuki K Poulose <suzuki.poulose@arm.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20220628173004.30002-2-mike.leach@linaro.org
